{
  "texts": [
    "The second implication is considering Attitude as a Predictor; The confirmation that attitude toward using ChatGPT significantly influences intention to use echoes the importance of individuals' subjective feelings and perceptions in the technology adoption process.",
    "The finding contributes to the ongoing discourse on the role of attitude in shaping user behavior.",
    "Moreover, the practical implications are as follows.",
    "Understanding the positive impact of perceived usefulness and ease of use implies that efforts to enhance these aspects of ChatGPT can lead to increased adoption among students.",
    "Developers and educators should focus on making the tool more practical and user-friendly to maximize its utility in educational settings."
  ]
}